Вакансія від 23 березня 2020
Marketing analyst
Smart Solutions
· VIP · Агенція
Пошук персоналу, HR;
50–250 співробітників
Київ
Повна зайнятість.
Досвід роботи від 2 років.
Вища освіта.
Опис вакансії
Our partner, a leader in the soft drink industry, is looking for Marketing Analyst.Purpose of the job:
Provide accurate and meaningful commercial insights to Senior management team in the areas of market share reporting, Consumer and Shopper data;
Lead the creation of descriptive analysis;
Take participation in Long Range Plan creation with providing the Insights;
Monthly performance analysis conclusion preparation delivery to Commercial Teams;
Responsibility for running regular and ad hoc reports base on Nielsen Retail Audit and other data sources;
Supporting other team members with in-depth understanding of research methodologies;
Lead onboarding process on insights relevant data bases.
Skills Knowledge:
Strong analytical skills which will allow generation of strong recommendations based on insights;
Good presentation skills and ability to present complex analysis in a friendly, digestible way;
Management and merging of different data sources;
Strong influencing, interpersonal and communication skills;
IT literate with effective skills in Excel (ideally advanced) and PowerPoint.
Experience Required:
University degree, economics, technical, IT or related field;
3+ years professional experience in Marketing Research (on agency or Client side) or Marketing;
Proficiency in using RMS Nielsen.
Company offers:
Meaningful work in a company that is leader in NARTD market;
Work in a smart and motivated team within a supportive and inclusive culture with strong values;
Competitive salary;
Compensation benefits package, which includes: medical insurance, meal allowance, company product sampling;
Corporate buses from metro stations: Chernigivska, Lybidska, Pochaina, Poznyaky.
